    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 requirements. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate adequate fidelity for identifying worst-case operating conditions. Relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion at all evaluated operating points. Assessment supports regulatory submission for Class II CPB device tolerance analysis.",
